A small fun map I made for my clan - Deagles only, but you will find some TMP's ;)

DOT_NIGHTHAWK_AZTEC
===================

Firstly, thanks to the original author of dot_nighthawk, whoever you are :)

A little conversion for Aztec fans!

Floor switches open doors to collect TMP's, but be careful, they are on the other side of the map.
